    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for a major project. It currently has significant engine trouble, including a suspected head gasket leak, and the transmission shifts harshly. The body shows extensive rust on the frame and wheel wells, and the interior has seen better days with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will need to be towed and requires substantial work before it can be safely driven on the road.",
